Package: gitter
Type: Package
Title: an R package for quantification of pinned microbial culture 
Version: 1.0.4
Date: 2014-01-23
Author: Omar Wagih, Leopold Parts
Maintainer: Omar Wagih <wagih@ebi.ac.uk>
Description: gitter is a image analysis package for R. Its primary goal is to allow users to robustly and quickly grid and quantify biological images of pinned colonies. It includes several image pre-processing techniques, such as autorotation of plates, noise removal, contrast adjustment and image resizing.
License: LGPL
Imports: jpeg, tiff, logging, parallel, PET, ggplot2, EBImage